Installation
sudo apt -y install podman

Version
podman version

UID 1 = 100000
UID 2 = 100001

useradd user1
useradd user2

Deploying Containers

podman list imagesSe: podman image ls

podman ps

podman ps -a

podman search httpd

Run a container:
podman run -it rhscl/httpd-24-rhel7 /bin/bash

podman run --name=www -d -p 8000:8080 rhscl/httpd-24-rhel7
See containers: podman ps -a

